{"tid":742161,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）煮意粉變左做粥","createTime":"2018-07-14T10:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T17:46:11.000Z","uid":192460,"like":17,"dislike":204,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"0a62f487dc5239a67acfbb7d0d7d30b49bb2fd7c","tid":742161,"uid":192460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"細佬我岩岩煮意粉<br />\n落意粉之後冇耐就滲啲白色野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過左幾分鐘之後就變左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/180953_df0eba7143146396b91290d4e0ab23cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F180953_df0eba7143146396b91290d4e0ab23cf.png&h=3be9a55e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/180957_73f1bf27cfc305fb753fe6335e28dcb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F180957_73f1bf27cfc305fb753fe6335e28dcb6.png&h=05a927aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自問都叫煮過無數次意粉，今次真係第一次見到呢舊野<br />\n<br />\n於是我睇下個包裝係咪過期<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/181434_cf3706f574d11ed8644270ffb3ca93e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F181434_cf3706f574d11ed8644270ffb3ca93e6.png&h=728e708f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢嗡乜鳩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4037be7c4420ed39be10daf80c7133df8c022de","tid":742161,"uid":156795,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4156d8adefc2b864164ea56386f5bbf5d61a98c6","tid":742161,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07